        "action": "Require socialising activities to be offered to people in care homes ",
        "additional_details": "Activities should be designed using an understanding of how not letting them have opportunities to socialise can lead to loneliness which can also impact bonds with family and friends leading to a great upset.",
        "background": "The Government should require care homes to offer certain activities and opportunities for the elderly to socialise while always being taken care off. ",
